Cell["\<\
Equations below derived from the geodesic equation and checked using the \
paper 2404\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9795547308319798`*^9, 
  3.979554746815835*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"370e569b-3bcb-4a1f-8471-\
